title: Sun Mobility Ties Up With cKers Finance To Accelerate MaaS - The Financial Express
content: Sun Mobility Ties Up With cKers Finance To Accelerate MaaS  The Financial Express
description: cKers Finance has provided a debt financing facility to SUN Mobility that will be used to accelerate the deployment of electric vehicles integrated with SUN Mobility’s swappable batteries as part of the company’s MaaS model.
